question.title: Proguard and Object extends Parcelable - Class not found when unmarshalling

node.contents: I'm releasing my apk. In debug mode, I have no error. When I sign my apk with Proguard, my app works til the fourth screen, where I have to deal with a Value Object Class that implement Parcelable
